Class HeFQUINEngineConfigReader

java.lang.Object
se.liu.ida.hefquin.engine.HeFQUINEngineConfigReader
public class HeFQUINEngineConfigReader extends Object
Reads an RDF description of a configuration for the HeFQUIN engine and creates a HeFQUINEngine object based on this configuration.
